    <description>A command-line interface for Jira Cloud. Manage issues, sprints, and workflows directly from your terminal.

Features:
- Create, view, update, and delete Jira issues
- Transition issues through workflows
- Manage sprint assignments
- Search with JQL queries
- Add and view comments

Binary: atk-jira.exe</description>
    <summary>Command-line interface for Jira Cloud</summary>
